The Canadian Mathematical Bulletin (French: Bulletin Canadien de Math√©matiques) is a mathematics journal, established in 1958 and published quarterly by the Canadian Mathematical Society. The current editors-in-chief of the journal are Antonio Lei and Javad Mashreghi.  The journal publishes short articles in all areas of mathematics that are of sufficient interest to the general mathematical public.

Abstracting and indexing
The journal is abstracted in:
Mathematical Reviews
Web of Science
Scopus
Zentralblatt MATH

